The '''Lucky Star''' was a rundown [[Casino/Legends|casino]] that was located in the [[Corellian Sector (Nar Shaddaa)/Legends|Corellian sector]] on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. In [[5 BBY/Legends|5 BBY]] [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] visited the place when he searched for his old friend [[Mako Spince]] on the Smugglers' Moon.

